xmount (0.7.4bwfla3) precise; urgency=medium

  * Add files required to build libxmount* modules (headers and .pc file).
  * Support quilt patches.
  * patch: Explicitly allow the qemu module to be writable.
  * patch: Globally export symbols from dlopen()ed shared objects.

 -- Thomas Liebetraut <thomas@bw-fla.uni-freiburg.de>  Fri, 06 Nov 2015 16:24:05 +0100

xmount (0.7.4bwfla2) precise; urgency=low

  * Add padding to VDI header, makes Qemu understand emulated VDI files.
  * Refactored and thoroughly incorporated writethrough support into the underlying libraries.
  * Allow for split images in writethrough mode.

 --  <thomas@bw-fla.uni-freiburg.de>  Thu, 29 Oct 2015 11:31:01 +0100

